      "special_instructions": "CRITICAL: Intellectual history is not a story of smooth transmission. Look for the ruptures, the creative misreadings, the suppressed alternatives. Ideas don't just flow from teacher to student - they get transformed, appropriated, and fought over. The most interesting finding is often what got lost or distorted in transmission."
    },
